---
description: Database migrations and admin scripts
globs:
  - scripts/**
---

Migration conventions:
- `scripts/migrate.ts` — manual SQL migrations using `better-sqlite3`
- Schema version tracked via `PRAGMA user_version`
- Run: `npm run migrate`
- Encryption logic is inlined in migration scripts (matches `encryption.service.ts`)
- Always use prepared statements
- Run scripts via `npm run script <file>`
